{"tid":2246753,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★澳門賀一誠派「定心丸」 稱明年續向合資格市民派一萬元","createTime":"2020-10-17T10:23:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-18T05:15:03.000Z","uid":19454,"like":20,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"32c3e5eb2989c8798961acb34a22f39120daf8c2","tid":2246753,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T10:23:15.000Z","msg":"澳門行政長官賀一誠稱，明年會繼續向每名合資格市民派發一萬元，但未決定發放形式。<br />\n<br />\n行政長官賀一誠派「定心丸」，稱明年會繼續每人派一萬元，但形式是派現金，還是以消費卡方式，還要研究。<br />\n<br />\n澳門行政長官賀一誠表示：「如果市民都是認為按照原來好，就按照原來的好。政府來說，不是說想搞甚麼事，再多一些麻煩的事出來，但希望整體經濟能夠帶動得到，這就是我們的想法。不會縮水，這是肯定不會縮水，一樣。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5f8a9a0934b031a706662f05/%E8%B3%80%E4%B8%80%E8%AA%A0%E7%A8%B1%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E7%BA%8C%E5%90%91%E5%90%88%E8%B3%87%E6%A0%BC%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E6%B4%BE%E4%B8%80%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83-%E6%9C%AA%E6%B1%BA%E5%AE%9A%E7%99%BC%E6%94%BE%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5f8a9a0934b031a706662f05%2F%25E8%25B3%2580%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%25AA%25A0%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E6%2598%258E%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%25BA%258C%25E5%2590%2591%25E5%2590%2588%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%25A0%25BC%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2585%2583-%25E6%259C%25AA%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E5%25AE%259A%25E7%2599%25BC%25E6%2594%25BE%25E5%25BD%25A2%25E5%25BC%258F&d=6FpmejEDNbHOA1ae24hao4sqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=dd0ab83a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5f8a9a0934b031a706662f05/%E8%B3%80%E4%B8%80%E8%AA%A0%E7%A8%B1%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E7%BA%8C%E5%90%91%E5%90%88%E8%B3%87%E6%A0%BC%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E6%B4%BE%E4%B8%80%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83-%E6%9C%AA%E6%B1%BA%E5%AE%9A%E7%99%BC%E6%94%BE%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F</a>"},{"pid":"ab7dfd2b72b52e94985f2b32fa636e5629c3e287","tid":2246753,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T10:23:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\